window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A murder has taken place in a tony Mumbai neighbourhood. A prime suspect, Prashanth, keeps his silence in the interrogation room as Inspector Khan plays the tapes of his therapy sessions. The explosive tapes, surreptitiously recorded by therapist Shaily Gupta, slowly reveal shocking information about Prashanth, about his relationship with his girlfriend Sonya, about the therapist and about the gruesome murder in question.<br> &nbsp;</p> <p>Put your earphones on and get in on the excitement of a twisted whodunnit thriller, <i>Play. Pause. Murder</i>., an OfSpin Original. Produced by OfSpin Media Friends.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"; 
